==================================================================================
|ID|OPERATOR              |NAME                            |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |DISTRIBUTED MERGE     |                                |3       |6           |
|1 |└─HASH JOIN           |                                |3       |6           |
|2 |  ├─TABLE FULL SCAN   |T1(GKEY)                        |3       |3           |
|3 |  └─SUBPLAN SCAN      |VIEW1                           |4       |3           |
|4 |    └─TABLE RANGE SCAN|T2(IDX_FOR_HEAP_GTT_SOURCETABLE)|4       |3           |
==================================================================================
